1 An ðæt ilce tunge ðe me ær gewundode,
2 ðæt hit me on ða ða oðre sidan gewende,
3 and ða eft ða læcedom me sealde;

10 Þær wæs lyt ðonne niht and lyt ðonne dæg,
11 swa ðæt ðæt gesihð me forð gewat lyt;
12 ac ic gehyrde ðær hlude horn blawan,

19 Ic wæs lyt gehworfen on ðære stede,
20 ða ðuhte me ðæt ic gesawe ðær torras swiðe heah;
21 ða cwæð ic: "Lareow, sege me, hwæt is ðeos stow?".

25 ðu gesyhst wel gif ðu ðærtogeþegnest,
26 hu ðæt gesihð bið swiðe gedwolen feorran;
27 forðæm ðe selfne ðu scealt lyt swiðor prician.

37 swa ðurh ða ðiccan lyft and ðone dimman,
38 nealæcande ðære strande swiðor and swiðor,
39 flugon fram me gedwimor and weoxon ege;

52 And gif heo ðara ylpende and ðara hwæla
53 ne onscunað, se ðe scearplice lociað,
54 rihtwisre and geradran heo ðæs teald;

61 ða ðe on niht beoð ofer heofenum gesiene,
62 ðonne hi scinað scip-flotan on sæ;
63 his teð wæron swa twegen wilde-swin,

64 ða ðe wudurofum wrotad on holt;
65 his lichoma wæs swa mære and swa micel
66 swa ðæs huses ðac ðe hæðnum men

76 Þa cwæð he to me: "Elli hire selfne wregð;
77 þes is Nembroð, ðurh ðæs yflan geþoht
78 an ðæt anlicnes ne bið on eorðan."

79 Læte we hine licgan and ne ceorfon ymbe;
80 forðæm him is æghwylc spræc
81 swylce his agen ðe nan man ne can.

94 He is nemned Fialte, and he worhte ða miclan dad
95 ða ða ða gigantas Gode wæron gram;
96 ða earmas ðe he ongann, he næfre eft ne onhrærð.

124 Ne læt ðu us faran to Titius ne to Typhon:
125 ðes mæg gifan ðæt ðe her is gewilnod;
126 forðæm gebig ðe and ne wend ðu ðinne nosu.

133 Firgilius, ða he hine gebundenne ongeat,
134 cwæð to me: "Gecyr ðu her, ðæt ic ðe genime";
135 ða dyde he swa ðæt he and ic wæron an byrðen.

142 Ac liðelice on ðone grund ðe forswealg
143 Lucifer mid Iudan, he us lædde;
144 ne, swa abugen, ðær ða wunode,
